rating_comment: The stay was at a very convenient location and had all the necessary amenities you would need to make yourself at home. Lots of shops nearby and rickshaws are easily available to all nearby spots. The caretaker was friendly and the host made the check in and booking process very convenient for us. The entrance has security camera so you can be assured about your safety, and any assistance required was rendered to. Would definitely book this place again in the future.
